name: Desert
LocationDStext: May not deploy to Bespin, Coruscant, Dagobah, Hoth, Kessel or Naboo. Your Jawas and Tusken Raiders may deploy here. Sandwhirl here moves only if on Tatooine.
LocationLStext: May not deploy to Bespin, Coruscant, Dagobah, Hoth, Kessel or Naboo. Each of your battle destiny draws is -1 here. Sandwhirl here moves only if on Tatooine.
